// config/product-status.json
// Controls the state of each product page.
//
// status options:
//   "coming-soon"   — hides buy button, shows waitlist form (no PDF ready)
//   "live"          — shows buy button (PDF ready + Razorpay connected)
//
// Change any product from "coming-soon" to "live" once:
//   1. The PDF is built and hosted/linked in DELIVERY_LINKS env var
//   2. Razorpay is approved (or Cashfree fallback configured)
//   3. End-to-end delivery is tested (buy → receive email → download works)
//
// AI Agent: NEVER change status from "coming-soon" to "live" automatically.
//           Request human approval via GitHub issue first.
